&Q000493 = An adab to Inana for Ur-Ninurta (Ur-Ninurta D)
@composite
#project: epsd2/literary
#atf: use unicode
#atf: use math
#etcsl: text-id=c.2.5.6.4
#key: after http://etcsl.orinst.ox.ac.uk/cgi-bin/etcsl.cgi?text=c.2.5.6.4&display=Crit&charenc=gcirc#

@div barsud A

1. in-nin₉ zag dib {d}a-nun-na-ke₄-ne me kilib₃-ba ur₄-ur₄#
#lem: innin[lady]; zag[side]; dib[pass]; Anunak[1]DN; me[Being]; kilib[total]; ur[gather]
#etcsl: line-id=A.1

2. igi-zu nir-ŋal₂ an ki-bi-da kur-kur-ra igi ŋal₂
#lem: igi[eye]; nirŋal[authoritative]; an[sky]; ki[place]; kur[mountain(s)]; igi[eye]; ŋal[⟦be⟧ to be (there]
#etcsl: line-id=A.2

3. {d}inana piriŋ an-na mul-mul-lu me-zu galam-galam-ma
#lem: Inanak[1]DN; piriŋ[lion]; an[sky]; mul[shine]; me[Being]; galam[skilful]
#etcsl: line-id=A.3

4. ŋarza-zu niŋ₂ nu-kur₂-ru-dam ŋiš-hur-zu dugud-da
#lem: ŋarza[rites]; niŋ[thing]; kur[different]; ŋešhur[plan]; dugud[heavy]
#etcsl: line-id=A.4

@div trailer 

5. bar-sud-am₃
#lem: barsud[musical notation]
#etcsl: line-id=A.5

@end trailer

@end barsud

@div sa-gida B

6. dim₂-ma-zu abzu su₃-ra₂-am₃ igi bar-re nu-um-zu
#lem: dimma[thought]; abzu[(cosmic) underground water]; sud[distant]; igi[eye]; bar[place outside]; zu[know]
#etcsl: line-id=B.6

7. a-ra₂ ak-a-zu niŋ₂ gal-gal-am₃ diŋir nu-me-da-sa₂
#lem: ara[way]; ak[do]; niŋ[thing]; gal[big]; diŋir[deity]; sa[equal]
#etcsl: line-id=B.7

8. me-zu ud silim-ma-bi ba-e-de₆ niŋ₂-nam la-ba-e-da-šub
#lem: me[Being]; ud[sun]; silim[healthy]; de[carry]; niŋnam[anything]; šub[fall]
#etcsl: line-id=B.8

9. nam-lugal zu₂ keše₂-me niŋ₂-nam-ma šu-zu la-ba-ra-e₃
#lem: namlugal[kingship]; zu[tooth]; kešed[bind]; niŋnam[anything]; šu[hand]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=B.9

10. an lugal-da zag mu-un-de₃-ša₄ nam mu-un-di-ni-ib-tar-re
#lem: An[1]DN; lugal[king]; zag[side]; sa[equal]; nam[fate]; tar[cut]
#etcsl: line-id=B.10

11. {d}en-lil₂-gin₇ ka-ta e₃-a-zu ki-bi-še₃ al-ŋa₂-ŋa₂
#lem: Enlil[1]DN; kag[mouth]; e[leave]; ki[place]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=B.11

12. {d}inana mah-di an ki-a gaba-ri nu-tuku-me-en
#lem: Inanak[1]DN; mahdi[exalted]; an[sky]; ki[place]; gabari[equal]; tuku[acquire]
#etcsl: line-id=B.12

13. lugal ki aŋ₂ diŋir-re-e-ne a-la mu-un-ši-ak-e#
#lem: lugal[king]; ki[place]; aŋ[measure]; diŋir[deity]; ala[exuberance]; ak[do]
#etcsl: line-id=B.13

14. {d}ur-{d}nin-urta šul igi il₂-la-zu me-te-zu-uš en-e
#lem: Urninurta[1]RN; šul[youth]; igi[eye]; il[raise]; mete[appropriate thing]; en[priest]
#etcsl: line-id=B.14

15. {d}nin-tur₅-re hi-li mu#-[un-ši]-in-tu#-ud-<<de₃-en>> u₆ [di-zu]-še₃# ma-ra-an-gub
#lem: Nintur[1]DN; hili[attractiveness]; utud[give birth (to)]; u[admiration]; di[speak]; gub[stand]
#etcsl: line-id=B.15

16. ŋiš-šub-ba-ni sag₉-ge mu-un#-[ge]-en# igi-za im-mi-in#-[...]
#lem: ŋeššub[lot]; sag[good]; gin[confirm]; igi[eye]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.16

17. ur₃-ra GA šu-nir-e he₂-du₇-a nam-nun-še₃ mu-un-il₂
#lem: ur[roof]; X; šunir[emblem]; hedu[ornament]; namnun[magnificence]; il[raise]
#etcsl: line-id=B.17

18. ir-sim dug₃-ga ku₇-ku₇-da-ke₄ šag₄ kug-zu he₂-em-tum₃
#lem: irsim[fragrance]; dug[good]; kud[sweet]; šag[heart]; kug[pure]; tum[bring]
#etcsl: line-id=B.18

19. ŋiš-nu₂ gi₄-rin hi-li si-a-za gu₂ hu-mu-un-di-X-re
#lem: ŋešnud[bed]; girim[flower]; hili[attractiveness]; si[fill]; gu[neck]; X
#etcsl: line-id=B.19

20. šul ŋiš tuku nun za-a-še₃ ŋal₂-la me ul-zu-uš ha-ba-gub
#lem: šul[youth]; ŋeš[tree]; tuku[acquire]; nun[prince]; zaʾe[you]; ŋal[⟦be⟧ to be (there]; me[Being]; zu[know]; gub[stand]
#etcsl: line-id=B.20

21. {d}ur-{d}nin-urta-ke₄ uŋ₃ šar₂-re us₂ zid he₂-bi₂-ib-dab₅-be₂
#lem: Urninurta[1]RN; uŋ[people]; šar[numerous]V/i; us[path]; zid[right]; dab[seize]
#etcsl: line-id=B.21

@div trailer 

22. sa-gid₂-da-am₃
#lem: sagida[musical notation]
#etcsl: line-id=B.22

@end trailer

@end sa-gida

@div jicgijal C

23. {d}inana {d}ur-{d}nin-urta-ke₄ ud ul da-ri₂-še₃ muš₃ la-ba-da-tum₂-mu
#lem: Inanak[1]DN; Urninurta[1]RN; ud[sun]; ul[distant time]; dari[eternal]; muš[face]; tum[bring]
#etcsl: line-id=C.23

@div trailer 

24. ŋiš-gi₄-ŋal₂-bi-im
#lem: ŋešgiŋal[musical refrain]
#etcsl: line-id=C.24

@end trailer

@end jicgijal

@div sa-jara D

25. {d}inana# nin an ki daŋal-la u₁₈-ru KI UD-ta
#lem: Inanak[1]DN; nin[lady]; an[sky]; ki[place]; daŋal[wide]; urun[exalted]; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=D.25

26. X [...] X-ma saŋ mu₂-mu₂-mu₂ ŋi₆ u₃-na kar₂-kar₂
#lem: X; X; X; saŋ[head]; mu[grow]; ŋi[night]; ŋiʾunak[night]; kar[blow]
#etcsl: line-id=D.26

27. [...] kur# idim-ta e₃-a an uraš-a daŋal bur₂
#lem: X; kur[mountain(s)]; idim[spring]; e[leave]; an[sky]; uraš[earth]; daŋal[wide]; bur[spread out]
#etcsl: line-id=D.27

28. [...]-da# teš₂-bi-im ama-na hi-li-bi-im
#lem: X; teš[(sense of) shame]; ama[mother]; hili[attractiveness]
#etcsl: line-id=D.28

29. [... he₂]-mi#-ni-in-mah-en ur-{d}nin-urta-ke₄
#lem: X; mah[great]; Urninurta[1]RN
#etcsl: line-id=D.29

30. [...] saŋ# hu-mu-ni-in-il₂ am gal-bi he₂-a
#lem: X; saŋ[head]; il[raise]; am[wild bull]; gal[big]; me[be]
#etcsl: line-id=D.30

31. [...] gam#-gam-mu-na-ab šu he₂-em-ri-ri-e
#lem: X; gurum[bend]; šu[hand]; ri[impose]
#etcsl: line-id=D.31

32. [a] zid#-da-ta ri-a-na šu mah-a-ni si-bi₂-ib
#lem: a[water]; zid[right]; ri[impose]; šu[hand]; mah[great]; si[fill]
#etcsl: line-id=D.32

33. uŋ₃# u₂-sal-la hu-mu-un-de₃-nu₂ na-gada-bi he₂-a
#lem: uŋ[people]; usal[meadow]; nud[lie down]; nagada[herdsman]; me[be]
#etcsl: line-id=D.33

